  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Art Therapy Workshop for Rehabilitating Soldiers</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For the last 9 years, every Wednesday our volunteers gather at the Rehab. Dept. at Tel Hashomer hospital, to offer war veterans a free Art Therapy Workshop.  Our &apos;art students&apos; are hospitalized for  months on end, far from home, struggling daily to return to their mental and physical abilities. They repeatedly tell us how the weekly art workshops are like a ray of sunlight in the hospital routine. We are seeking funds only for the purchase of the canvases, paint, brushes &amp; easels.</narrative>
  </description>
